288
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,830
Who sent the letter?

289
00:17:24,330 --> 00:17:26,480
Someone by the name of Grimmer.

290
00:17:27,530 --> 00:17:28,170
What did you say?

291
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:32,830
We've already put a warrant out for
Grimmer as the prime suspect.

292
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,800
W-Wait a minute!

293
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:37,590
It's okay now, Suk.

294
00:17:37,610 --> 00:17:41,970
Detective Zeman's murder, the
commissioner's poisoning...

295
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:44,210
and the special task force murders...

296
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:47,190
have now all been resolved.

297
